Package de.ovgu.softwareprojekt.pipeline.splitters

This package contains the pipeline splitters that have already been implemented.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ClientSensorSplitter
    This class combines the functionality of SensorSplitter and ClientSplitter, that is, data sinks can be registered to be notified only of specified sensor type events from specified network devices
    ClientSplitter
    This class can be used to split data from various devices to different pipelines.
    PipelineDuplication
    This splitter will clone the pipeline data to each added data sink.
    SensorSplitter
    This filter splits data by sensor type to specified pipelines.
    Switch
    This pipeline splitter forwards incoming data to one of two data sinks.

Package de.ovgu.softwareprojekt.pipeline.splitters Description

This package contains the pipeline splitters that have already been implemented. Splitters are used to redirect data depending on certain conditions, like which client the data is from.
